     <h4>Checklist to apply for DSC</h4>
<h6>Indian Individuals Looking to Obtain DSC Must Submit:</h6>
<ul class="a">
    <li>1. ID proof: Passport/Driving license or any Photo Identity issued by the Govt</li>
    <li>2. PAN card</li>
    <li>3. Address proof: Aadhaar card/Voter ID/Driving license/Registration Certificate</li>
    <li>4. Attesting Officer proof</li>
</ul>
<h6>Indian Organizations Looking to Get DSC Must Submit:</h6>
<ul>
    <li>1.	Organizational PAN</li>
    <li>2.	Partnership deed, if applicable</li>
    <li>3.	List of Authorised Signatories which could be the list of Directors, Board resolution, etc.</li>
    <li>4.	Authorised Signatory ID proof</li>
    <li>5.	GST certificate</li>

</ul>
